-- Royal Bafokeng Platinum Revives Plan to List in Johannesburg as Talks End
-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 2010-10-11T10:20:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-11/royal-bafokeng-platinum-revives-plan-to-list-in-johannesburg-as-talks-end.html
Royal Bafokeng Platinum Ltd. said it
is continuing with its plan to list on the main board of the
stock exchange in Johannesburg during the final quarter of the
year after talks with an unidentified party were terminated.  Royal Bafokeng Platinum commented in an e-mailed statement
today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
